The pieces are beginning to fall into place.

873
00:55:01,844 --> 00:55:04,312
I don't have one anymore.

874
00:55:04,413 --> 00:55:06,381
Well, that's less important.

875
00:55:06,482 --> 00:55:10,476
I mean, so-so - sociologically,
I mean, what's important is...

876
00:55:10,587 --> 00:55:13,419
having grown up with the assumption
of material security.

877
00:55:13,522 --> 00:55:16,185
It - It explains a lot.

878
00:55:16,292 --> 00:55:18,192
I call.

879
00:55:19,696 --> 00:55:21,597
