895
00:56:12,853 --> 00:56:15,378
- I don't know what it could be.
- You don't?

896
00:56:15,489 --> 00:56:17,116
No.

897
00:56:19,193 --> 00:56:22,561
One word - "stepmother. "

898
00:56:25,099 --> 00:56:28,364
Well, I hope I can talk to them
